Copyright (c) 2026 MemoryAI

This product includes engineering workflow content adapted from
"agent-skills" by Addy Osmani (https://github.com/addyosmani/agent-skills),
licensed under MIT.

Adapted content lives in:
  - rules/skills/         (workflow definitions, restructured to TOML)
  - rules/personas/       (persona definitions, restructured to TOML)
  - references/           (security, performance, accessibility checklists)

Coding-Guard adds:
  - 9 enforced rules with predicates and severity gates (block/warn)
  - Per-platform fan-out across 11 IDE/CLI targets
  - Anti-rationalization tables, red-flags arrays, and evidence
    requirements wired to runtime hooks
  - Ed25519 signing and lineage chain (constitution.toml.sig)

